    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR. This CT9A chassis remains in concours condition, featuring the legendary 4G63 power plant with its original MHI TD05HR-16G6C-10.5T twin-scroll turbocharger. The drivetrain is impeccable; the Active Center Differential (ACD) and 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission operate with factory-new precision. It retains the MR-exclusive Bilstein monotube dampers and forged BBS alloy wheels, which are free of any oxidation or curb rash. The exterior finish exhibits consistent micron depth across all panels, and the interior bolsters show zero compression or wear. This is a mechanically perfect, bone-stock example for the discerning collector who demands a turn-key, high-performance icon.",
